caseout.tip12: Ko e tuʻasila fakalotofonuá ko e tuʻasila USDT ia ke toʻo mei aí. Kātaki ʻo fakapapauʻi ʻa e tuʻasila ʻokú ke fakaʻaongaʻi fakaleleí, ʻe iku e fehālākí ki he mole mo e paʻanga ʻoku ʻikai lava ke fakaʻaongaʻí

caseout.tip15: Koeʻuhi ke lava ʻo fakapapauʻi ʻoku malu ʻa e paʻanga, ʻe fakahoko ʻe he tauʻanga lelue ha fakatokanga ʻoku tuʻu fakatuʻutamaki ki he toho takitaha, pea ʻe toe vakaiʻi nima pe ha ngaahi toho ʻe niʻihi. Kātaki ʻo tatali ʻi he faʻa kātaki. He ʻikai kole atu ʻe he kau ngāue ki he kakaʻangá ha lea fufū ki he polokalamá.
caseout.tip16: Hili hoʻo fakatau, ʻoku fie maʻu ke ke tatali ʻi ha ʻaho ʻe 1 ke toho ha paʻanga. Kapau ʻoku ʻi ai haʻo fehuʻi, kātaki ʻo fetuʻutaki ki heʻemau tokoni ki he kasitomaá.
